4-6  地域別自動車保有台数及び有料駐車場数 (平成26年度末)
登録自動車台数及び課税登録台数（軽自動車）には，外国軍人軍属の私有車を含む。 また， 駐車場は駐車場法に基づき
届けられた500㎡以上のものである。
注 1) 総排気量が250㏄を超えるオートバイなど。
2) 軽自動車の登録台数は年度当初の課税台数である。
資料： (財)自動車検査登録情報協会，都総務局行政部区政課，都建設局道路管理部管理課
4-6  NUMBER OF MOTOR VEHICLES AND PAY PARKING LOTS BY DISTRICT
Motor vehicles registered and "Light four-wheeled motor vehicles registered" include private vehicles owned by foreign military and civilian
personnel.  "Pay parking lots" refer to those with an area of at least 500㎡ reported as regulated under the Parking Lot Act.
Note: 1) Such as motorcycles with a displacement of over 250cc.
2) The number of light four-wheeled motor vehicles registered is the number of such vehicles taxed as of the beginning of the fiscal year.
Source: Automobile Inspection and Registration Information Association; Bureau of General Affairs，TMG;BureauofConstruction，TMG
